{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197/events","html_url":"https://github.com/pugjs/pug/issues/197","id":738080,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3MzgwODA=","number":197,"title":"Indentation issue with :coffeescript filter puts code in the wrong scope","user":{"login":"focusaurus","id":482377,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ4MjM3Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/482377?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus","html_url":"https://github.com/focusaurus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/focusaurus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":4,"created_at":"2011-04-06T15:28:01Z","updated_at":"2011-06-01T17:02:39Z","closed_at":"2011-06-01T17:02:39Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When I have this markup inside a jade template:\n\n```\n:coffeescript\n  window.outer = ->\n    inner = ->\n      alert(\"This is inner line 1\")\n      alert(\"This is inner line 2\")\n```\n\nIt gets incorrectly compiled to this:\n\n```\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n(function() {\n  window.outer = function() {\n    var inner;\n    inner = function() {\n      return alert(\"This is inner line 1\");\n    };\n    return alert(\"This is inner line 2\");\n  };\n}).call(this);\n</script>\n```\n\nNote how the \"This is inner line 2\" has been un-indented by one level thus putting it in the wrong function scope.  Coffeescript itself doesn't do this.  The workaround is to indent that line by an extra 2 spaces.\n","closed_by":{"login":"tj","id":25254,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI1MjU0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25254?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj","html_url":"https://github.com/tj","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tj/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/197/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}